        <div class="tp-comp-text"><strong>"N&#8322; washout systematically underestimates lung volumes in COPD and asthma patients."</strong> Gas can't reach air trapped behind narrowed airways. MiniBox+ plethysmography measures ALL gas in the thorax — truer disease picture, and you bill the higher CPT 94726 instead of 94727.</div>
