      <div class="card-body" style="color:#5b21b6;">This tab is scaffolded per Avi's request. Each card below shows the intended structure. Replace bracketed [placeholders] with actual company URLs, contacts, policy links, and screenshots once confirmed with Sales Ops, Finance, and IT.</div>
