          <div style="margin-bottom:6px;"><strong>Where:</strong> Account &rarr; Activities &rarr; Log a Call.</div>
          <div style="margin-bottom:6px;"><strong>Required fields:</strong> Date, Attendees, Discipline, Discussion Topic, Next Step, Next Step Date.</div>
          <div><strong>Tip:</strong> Attach competitive intel to the Account Notes, not the call record.</div>
        </div>
