    <div class="card-grid grid-2" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
      <div class="card" style="border-left:4px solid #dc2626;">
        <div class="card-title">&#128737; Code of Conduct</div>
        <div class="card-body">Professional behavior, customer interactions, anti-harassment, anti-discrimination, conflicts of interest, gift &amp; entertainment limits.<br><strong>Full document:</strong> [link] &middot; <strong>Owner:</strong> HR</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="border-left:4px solid #dc2626;">
        <div class="card-title">&#9878; Healthcare Compliance</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div style="margin-bottom:4px;"><strong>HIPAA:</strong> No PHI on personal devices. Encrypted laptop required.</div>
          <div style="margin-bottom:4px;"><strong>Sunshine Act:</strong> Log all HCP spend &gt; $[XX].</div>
          <div style="margin-bottom:4px;"><strong>FDA:</strong> On-label only. No off-label claims.</div>
          <div><strong>AdvaMed Code:</strong> Meal/educational-item limits.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="border-left:4px solid #ea580c;">
        <div class="card-title">&#128737; Anti-Bribery / FCPA</div>
        <div class="card-body">No payments, gifts, or favors intended to influence a purchase decision. Annual training required. Escalate anything ambiguous.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="border-left:4px solid #ea580c;">
        <div class="card-title">&#128188; Travel &amp; Expense</div>
        <div class="card-body">See rules in the top half of this tab. Weekly submission, receipts &gt; $[XX], hotel cap $[XXX], lowest logical air fare.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">&#127968; PTO &amp; Leave</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div style="margin-bottom:4px;"><strong>Accrual:</strong> [XX] days/year.</div>
          <div style="margin-bottom:4px;"><strong>Request:</strong> [HRIS URL] &mdash; 2 weeks notice preferred.</div>
          <div><strong>Parental / Medical Leave:</strong> [policy link]</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">&#128737; Sample, Demo &amp; Loaners</div>
        <div class="card-body">Track every device movement in [system]. Loaner duration: [XX] days max. Evaluation units require signed eval agreement. <strong>Damaged/lost:</strong> notify Ops within 24 hrs.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">&#128274; IT Security &amp; Device Use</div>
        <div class="card-body">Company laptop only for work. MFA required. VPN on non-corporate networks. No customer data in personal email / cloud. <strong>Lost device:</strong> call IT immediately.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">&#128680; Incident Reporting</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div style="margin-bottom:4px;"><strong>Adverse event / device complaint:</strong> Report to Quality within [XX] hours. [Form URL]</div>
          <div style="margin-bottom:4px;"><strong>Customer complaint:</strong> Log in SF + CC Sales Ops.</div>
          <div><strong>Compliance hotline:</strong> [anonymous hotline / URL]</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">&#128663; Company Vehicle</div>
        <div class="card-body">[Allowance] or [lease program]. Valid license + annual MVR check. <strong>Accident:</strong> [phone] &rarr; Safety.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">&#127891; Training &amp; Certification</div>
        <div class="card-body"><strong>Annual:</strong> HIPAA, Code of Conduct, AdvaMed, Cybersecurity. <strong>On hire:</strong> Product cert, Salesforce 101. <strong>LMS:</strong> [platform URL]</div>
      </div>
    </div>

