    </div>

    <!-- ============ VIEW: FILES & TEMPLATES ============ -->
    <div id="allergy-view-files" class="alp" style="display:none;">
      <div class="alp-lede">Every allergy leave-behind in one place &mdash; the &ldquo;Will You Get Paid?&rdquo; coverage &amp; coding guide, the brochure, the CHEST 2021 validation, the sample report and more. <strong>View</strong> reads it, <strong>Download</strong> saves it, <strong>Email it</strong> jumps to the Email Center with the file attached &mdash; no manual attaching.</div>
