    <!-- ============ THE PITCH ============ -->
    <div class="fin-view" id="fin-view-pitch">
      <div class="fin-pitch-lede">
        <strong>Price is the #1 stall &mdash; and the easiest one to erase.</strong><br>
        A MiniBox lab bills more each month than it costs to finance. Turn every price objection into a monthly number and the practice is cash-flow positive from the very first test.
      </div>
      <div class="fin-quote">
        &#128172; <b>The opener:</b> &ldquo;You never have to write a big check. We can put a complete pulmonary function lab in your office for a simple monthly payment &mdash; and a handful of tests a week more than covers it. Want me to show you the options?&rdquo;
      </div>
      <h3 style="font-size:15px;margin:18px 0 8px;color:#0f1b2d;">Three ways to finance &mdash; which to reach for</h3>
      <div class="fin-3">
        <div class="fin-mini"><div class="n">&#128184; NewLane Finance</div><div class="d">A clean monthly number for the doctor; PulmOne gets paid in full up front. Best when the practice just wants a simple monthly payment and a fast yes.</div></div>
        <div class="fin-mini"><div class="n">&#127974; Group Financial Services</div><div class="d">40+ year healthcare lender. Up to 5-year terms, 100% financing, up to 6-month deferred first payment. Best for longer terms or deferral.</div></div>
        <div class="fin-mini"><div class="n">&#127968; PulmOne in-house</div><div class="d">Lease-to-own $0 down, 0% up-to-12-month split-pay ($15,000 upfront), or a flat subscription. Best when the doctor wants to deal directly with us.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="fin-best" style="margin-top:14px;">
        <b>Objection &mdash; &ldquo;the upfront cost is a stretch&rdquo;:</b> &ldquo;Totally fair &mdash; nobody buys it with a check. $0 down, and the monthly payment is less than what a few tests a week reimburse. It pays for itself and then some.&rdquo; Then walk them through the monthly options under <b>All Options</b>.
      </div>
    </div>



    <!-- ============ ROI PROPOSAL BUILDER (v2.5, embedded from materials/) ============ -->
    <div class="fin-view" id="fin-view-calc" style="display:none;">
    <div style="background:#eff6ff; border:1px solid #bfdbfe; border-radius:10px; padding:12px 16px; margin-bottom:14px; font-size:12.5px; color:#1e3a8a;">
      &#9432; This is the full <strong>ROI Proposal Builder</strong> &mdash; cash, finance, or lease, plus the <strong>Section&nbsp;179</strong> deduction, warranty, five-year projection, and a printable proposal you can leave behind or email. Estimates only; final financing numbers come from the lender, and Section&nbsp;179 figures are not tax advice.
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:12px;">
      <button type="button" class="finsub-btn" onclick="roiBuilderFullscreen()">&#9974; Fullscreen</button>
      <button type="button" class="finsub-btn" onclick="roiBuilderPrint()">&#128424; Print / PDF</button>
      <a class="finsub-btn" href="materials/MiniBox-ROI-Proposal-Builder.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">&#8599; Open in a new tab</a>
    </div>
    <iframe id="roi-builder-iframe" title="MiniBox+ ROI Proposal Builder"
      src="materials/MiniBox-ROI-Proposal-Builder.html" loading="lazy" allow="clipboard-write; fullscreen"
      style="width:100%; border:0; height:1650px; display:block; background:#f1f5f9; border-radius:12px;"></iframe>
    </div><!-- /fin-view-calc -->

    <!-- ============ ALL OPTIONS ============ -->
    <div class="fin-view" id="fin-view-options" style="display:none;">

      <div class="fin-card">
        <span class="fin-tag partner">Independent lender</span>
        <h3>GE Healthcare Financial Services (HFS)</h3>
        <div style="font-size:13px;color:#475569;line-height:1.55;">One of the biggest names in medical-equipment financing, backed by GE Healthcare. Coverage is assigned by U.S. territory &mdash; three GE HFS reps split the country. Find the practice's region and reach the rep who covers it.</div>
        <ul class="fin-terms">
          <li><b>Territory-based</b> &middot; a dedicated GE HFS rep for each U.S. region</li>
          <li>Equipment financing &amp; lease structures for practices</li>
          <li>Institutional lender &mdash; strong option for larger or multi-site groups</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="fin-best"><b>Best for:</b> practices that want a big-name institutional lender, or when you already have a GE HFS relationship in that territory. See the coverage map, the deal process, and rep contacts on the <b>GE HFS</b> tab.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="fin-card">
        <span class="fin-tag vendor">Vendor financing</span>
        <h3>NewLane Finance</h3>
        <div style="font-size:13px;color:#475569;line-height:1.55;">The doctor pays a simple monthly payment. NewLane pays PulmOne in full within days of the sale and collects the monthly payments directly &mdash; no waiting on the practice, no collection risk.</div>
        <ul class="fin-terms">
          <li><b>Finance-to-own</b> &middot; <b>24 / 36 / 48 / 60-month</b> terms quoted for MiniBox+ deals &middot; you own the equipment at the end of the term</li>
          <li><b>No Payments for 90 Days</b> option &mdash; deal closes today, first payment after the machine is already billing</li>
          <li><b>Fast credit decisions</b> &mdash; apply in minutes, answer often within hours, not days</li>
          <li><b>Soft credit check</b> to pre-qualify &mdash; doesn&rsquo;t ding the doctor&rsquo;s credit score</li>
          <li><b>100% online</b> &middot; e-sign the documents, equipment ships to the door</li>
          <li><b>Section&nbsp;179 eligible</b> &mdash; the equipment may be tax-deductible and free up cash</li>
          <li>Works with a range of business credit profiles</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="fin-best"><b>Best for:</b> price-sensitive practices that just want a clean monthly payment and a fast yes. NewLane Finance is a subsidiary of WSFS Bank and has financed $1.1B+ in equipment.</div>
        <div class="fin-contact"><b>Carlos Cappuccio</b> &middot; Sr. Business Development Account Manager &ndash; Healthcare &middot; <a href="mailto:ccappuccio@newlanefinance.com">ccappuccio@newlanefinance.com</a> &middot; 609-280-4733 &middot; <a href="https://newlanefinance.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">newlanefinance.com</a><br>Application on the <b>Apply &amp; Contacts</b> tab &mdash; or run the numbers on the <b>ROI &amp; Proposal Builder</b> tab.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="fin-card">
        <span class="fin-tag partner">Independent lender</span>
        <h3>Group Financial Services (GfS)</h3>
        <div style="font-size:13px;color:#475569;line-height:1.55;">A complete lending resource for healthcare professionals for 40+ years. The practice applies directly and GfS finances the equipment.</div>
        <ul class="fin-terms">
          <li><b>Repayment terms up to 5 years</b></li>
          <li><b>100% financing</b> &middot; $10,000 minimum purchase</li>
          <li><b>Deferred first payment</b> up to 6 months</li>
          <li><b>Same-day approvals</b> &middot; quick short application</li>
          <li>Other terms &amp; structures available on request</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="fin-best"><b>Best for:</b> doctors who want longer terms, deferral, or a straightforward apply-and-own path. Subject to good credit + minimum 2-year license verification.</div>
        <div class="fin-contact"><b>Helen Giotopoulos Kaminski</b> &middot; <a href="mailto:helen@finservices.com">helen@finservices.com</a> &middot; 800-232-7526 &middot; <a href="https://www.groupfinancial.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">groupfinancial.com</a><br>Grab the application on the <b>Apply &amp; Contacts</b> tab.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="fin-card">
        <span class="fin-tag house">PulmOne direct</span>
        <h3>PulmOne in-house options</h3>
        <ul class="fin-terms">
          <li><b>Lease-to-Own &mdash; $0 down:</b> 12 / 24 / 36 / 60-month terms &middot; optional 90-day payment deferral &middot; $1 buyout at end of term.</li>
          <li><b>0% Financing &mdash; up to 12 months:</b> $7,500 at signing &middot; $7,500 at installation (<b>$15,000 upfront</b>) &middot; 0% on the remaining balance over up to 12 equal monthly payments.</li>
          <li><b>Subscription:</b> one fixed monthly cost covers the device and filters &mdash; no large capital outlay.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- ============ APPLY & CONTACTS ============ -->
    <div class="fin-view" id="fin-view-apply" style="display:none;">
      <div class="fin-card">
        <h3>How to get a practice financed</h3>
        <ol style="font-size:13.5px;color:#1e293b;line-height:1.7;padding-left:20px;margin:8px 0 0;">
          <li><b>Reframe to a monthly number.</b> Lead with the monthly payment, never the sticker price &mdash; finance-to-own turns the system into one manageable monthly number.</li>
          <li><b>Pick the lane.</b> Simple monthly payment &rarr; NewLane. Longer term / deferral / apply-and-own &rarr; Group Financial. Wants to deal with us directly &rarr; PulmOne in-house.</li>
          <li><b>Submit the application.</b> For Group Financial, complete the Quick Application below (one per legal owner) and fax or email it in &mdash; same-day approvals. For NewLane, complete the NewLane application below and email it back to Carlos.</li>
          <li><b>Approval &amp; ship.</b> On approval, terms are confirmed and PulmOne ships. First payment (unless deferred) plus a small processing fee is due with the final contract.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="fin-card">
        <h3>&#128196; Group Financial &mdash; Quick Application (2025)</h3>
        <div style="font-size:13px;color:#475569;margin-bottom:12px;">Open it, download it, or email it straight to the practice.</div>
        <div id="fin-apply-cards"></div>
        <div class="fin-contact" style="margin-top:14px;">
