          Office 800-232-7526 &middot; Fax 888-366-2398 &middot; Cell 404-512-4361 &middot; <a href="https://www.groupfinancial.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">groupfinancial.com</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="fin-card">
        <h3>&#128184; NewLane Finance &mdash; Application (2026)</h3>
        <div style="font-size:13px;color:#475569;margin-bottom:12px;">The one-page healthcare financing application. Complete it on screen, sign, and email it back to Carlos. NewLane runs a fast, soft-pull credit check (often an answer within hours), handles approval, and pays PulmOne up front &mdash; the practice just makes one monthly payment.</div>
        <div id="fin-apply-newlane"></div>
