          <b>Apply / questions:</b> Carlos Cappuccio &middot; Sr. Business Development Account Manager &ndash; Healthcare<br>
          <a href="mailto:ccappuccio@newlanefinance.com">ccappuccio@newlanefinance.com</a> &middot; Cell 609-280-4733 &middot; <a href="https://newlanefinance.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">newlanefinance.com</a><br>
          123 S. Broad Street, 17th Fl, Philadelphia, PA 19109 &middot; a division of WSFS Bank
        </div>
