    </div>
    <!-- ============ GE HFS ============ -->
    <div class="fin-view" id="fin-view-gehfs" style="display:none;">
      <div style="font-size:13.5px;color:#334155;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:14px;">Financing a practice through <b>GE Healthcare Financial Services</b> &mdash; the deal flow and the three GE reps who cover the country by territory.</div>
      <div class="fin-card">
        <h3>How a deal funds through GE HFS</h3>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#92400e;background:#fef3c7;border-radius:8px;padding:9px 12px;margin:8px 0 14px;line-height:1.5;">&#128221; <b>Working draft</b> &mdash; this is the flow we're laying out for financing a practice through GE Healthcare Financial Services. Confirm the exact steps (and DocuSign setup) with GE before it goes live.</div>
        <div class="fin-step"><div class="num">1</div><div class="body"><b>Build the quote.</b> Use the MiniBox+ Quote Builder (Forms tab) to put together the equipment quote for the practice.</div></div>
        <div class="fin-step"><div class="num">2</div><div class="body"><b>Send it to your GE HFS rep.</b> Email the quote to the rep who covers the practice's territory (contacts + map below).</div></div>
        <div class="fin-step"><div class="num">3</div><div class="body"><b>GE reviews &amp; sends terms back.</b> GE HFS runs credit and returns the approval and financing paperwork to us.</div></div>
        <div class="fin-step"><div class="num">4</div><div class="body"><b>DocuSign to the practice.</b> The finance agreement goes to the doctor for e-signature.</div></div>
        <div class="fin-step"><div class="num">5</div><div class="body"><b>Funded &mdash; PulmOne gets paid.</b> On signed docs + approval, GE funds the deal and PulmOne is paid up front; the practice pays GE monthly.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="fin-card">
        <h3>&#127974; GE Healthcare Financial Services &mdash; find your rep</h3>
        <div style="font-size:13px;color:#475569;margin-bottom:12px;line-height:1.55;">GE HFS assigns coverage by U.S. territory. Locate the practice's region on the map, then contact the rep for that zone.</div>
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="GE Healthcare Financial Services U.S. territory coverage map" style="width:100%;max-width:660px;display:block;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:10px;margin:0 auto 14px;">
        <div class="fin-3">
