            <div style="font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.5;"><a href="mailto:Mary.ban@gehealthcare.com" style="color:#0f4a85;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">Mary.ban@gehealthcare.com</a><br>262-794-7578</div>
          </div>
