            <div style="font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.5;"><a href="mailto:Matthew.salamon@gehealthcare.com" style="color:#0f4a85;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">Matthew.salamon@gehealthcare.com</a><br>203-241-8600</div>
