            <div style="font-size:12px;color:#475569;margin-bottom:6px;line-height:1.4;">Dallas &middot; Houston &middot; Atlanta &middot; Carolinas &middot; Florida &middot; South</div>
            <div style="font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.5;"><a href="mailto:Jeffrey.andrews@gehealthcare.com" style="color:#0f4a85;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">Jeffrey.andrews@gehealthcare.com</a><br>770-630-5742</div>
