        <div style="font-size:12px;color:#92400e;background:#fef3c7;border-radius:8px;padding:9px 12px;margin-top:12px;line-height:1.5;">&#9888; The <b>map above is the source of truth</b>. The territory-to-rep groupings listed here are read from the coverage slide &mdash; confirm the exact region split before relying on it.</div>
